in my room.

334
00:20:14,647 --> 00:20:18,718
No, I don't have another copy,
but I do have your copy.

335
00:20:21,788 --> 00:20:23,623
How did you get this?

336
00:20:23,656 --> 00:20:27,294
I found it on the floor
after class.

337
00:20:27,327 --> 00:20:29,262
It must be yours, right?

338
00:20:29,296 --> 00:20:31,331
Yeah. Thanks.

339
00:20:37,069 --> 00:20:42,742
You didn't happen to find
a bookmark in here, did you?

340
00:20:42,775 --> 00:20:47,314
