Not a chance.

382
00:23:03,015 --> 00:23:06,052
Their focus is elsewhere,
as should yours be.

383
00:23:06,085 --> 00:23:09,789
Why me? I mean,
why are you doing this for me?

384
00:23:09,822 --> 00:23:12,492
Because I see myself
in you, Bridgette,

385
00:23:12,525 --> 00:23:14,694
And I don't want you
to end up like me.

386
00:23:14,727 --> 00:23:16,496
We both deserve
better than that.

387
00:23:16,529 --> 00:23:18,631
But you're a teacher
at one of the most prestigious

388
00:23:18,665 --> 00:23:19,966
