And toddlers to count.

392
00:23:26,005 --> 00:23:29,709
So I'm just a toddler
to you?

393
00:23:29,742 --> 00:23:31,511
Quite the opposite.

394
00:23:31,544 --> 00:23:34,781
You're a young woman
full of great promise.

395
00:23:34,814 --> 00:23:38,551
You are the exception
to every rule.

396
00:23:38,585 --> 00:23:39,919
People like you are rare,

397
00:23:39,952 --> 00:23:42,555
But I know greatness
when I see it.

398
00:23:42,589 --> 00:23:44,891
We all have a purpose
in this life.

399
00:23:44,924 --> 00:23:46,225
You were meant to lead others,

400
00:23:46,258 --> 00:23:47,960
And I was meant to help
people like you

401
00:23:47,994 --> 00:23:50,062
Become the leaders
you were born to be.

402
00:23:50,096 --> 00:23:52,131
That's just the way it is.

403
00:23:54,901 --> 00:23:56,936
[Snickers]
