405
00:24:15,588 --> 00:24:18,691
I hope I'll be seeing you
for the Future Elite Party

406
00:24:18,725 --> 00:24:21,694
In a couple of weeks.
Bobby will be there, too.

407
00:24:21,728 --> 00:24:23,896
It's sure to be
a memorable evening.

408
00:25:55,287 --> 00:25:57,990
[Door opens]
Oh! You scared me.

409
00:25:58,024 --> 00:25:59,258
Sorry.

410
00:26:00,927 --> 00:26:02,194
Working on your English essay?

411
00:26:02,228 --> 00:26:03,596
Yeah.

412
00:26:03,630 --> 00:26:05,064
Wow, you wrote
a lot of notes.

413
00:26:05,097 --> 00:26:07,600
Yeah, yeah. I did.

414
00:26:07,634 --> 00:26:09,368
Okay.

415
00:26:09,401 --> 00:26:12,705
No, I'm just...
I'm glad to see you're, like,

